[Student "S"]
{NORTH has 18 points and a 5-card \H suit. This is a good hand 
to open 1\H.

SOUTH has three \Hs which is adequate support. But SOUTH only
has 4 points which is not strong enough to respond. So SOUTH passes.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "EW"]
[Deal "E:QJ964.A9.K74.KQJ T75.J8762.AT95.A K82.K543.86.9832 A3.QT.QJ32.T7654"]
